      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward transportation with plenty of usable life left for the right buyer. This vehicle is being offered as an honest-value option for someone who wants dependable basic mobility without a big upfront cost. A sensible choice for commuting, a first car, or a backup vehicle, it delivers strong budget appeal and real everyday usefulness at an accessible price.",
