      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly ride or a solid project to tinker with? This car is a great opportunity for someone who doesn\u2019t mind giving it a little love. It\u2019s got plenty of character, and with the right owner it could make a fun fixer-upper, commuter, or useful parts donor. If you\u2019re handy or just want something affordable to work with, this one is worth a look.",
